  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The only marks she has from the mosquito bites, and there was lots and lots of mosquitoes in the forest, because there was swamps there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that's how she-- she grew very healthy, no problems whatsoever-- the babies, no vaccinations, and no-- no formulas.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And no proper clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Very-- very, very nicely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This base which was a shtetl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, it was the headquarters of the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was an infectious disease hospital in the other base and there was people--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What we did, because we were a family at triad, and so didn't consider us as fighters, you know-- the Russians they made-- put pressure on us to be more-- more army-like than family-like.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We put more-- more accent on surviving and rescuing, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And giving fugitives from the ghettos, from the [NON-ENGLISH] our protection, more than to fight the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What could we do against the Germans?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we did had-- had so many fighters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We gave away 120 fighters who went to and formed a special group.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to have-- give concessions to the Russian partisan, because they were fighting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They expected us to fight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were under their command.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what we did instead, was giving them-- making-- providing them with sausages, with tradesmen, with bootmakers, with repair of the-- of the rifles and the arms, and baking for them bread.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So every day, because we were in the zemilyankas from all the trees, took charge of the provisions, were in one zemilyankas.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And most of the transactions went in our zemilyankas.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They come from the other things-- they ordered so many loaves of bread, so many kilos of sausage, so many of ham.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
